This paper discusses the Residual Network (ResNet) architecture, which is commonly used in computer vision tasks (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses weight initialization, which is a fundamental aspect of neural network training and optimization (cs.NE). The paper presents experimental results and analysis, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
